snippet.title: Rayman 3 Intro/ Promo/ Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
This is basically my childhood and I love this trailer they have at the beginning of the game. It brings back memories from the era of the GameCube and I really hope they make a Rayman 4 not these Rayman Raging Rabbits games!!!
Heres to Rayman 3!!!
If you enjoyed please leave me a like and i am posting content often so if you wanna subscribe! THANKS!!!

Song: Madder
Artist: Groove Armada
